name: Timelord Progenitor Vulgate
desc:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
Cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects. You take no battle damage from attacks involving this card. At the end of the Damage Step, if this card Special Summoned from the Extra Deck battled: You can banish all monsters your opponent controls, also, for the rest of this turn, any battle damage your opponent takes is halved. Once per turn, during the End Phase, if this effect was activated this turn: Special Summon as many monsters that you banished by that effect as possible to your opponent's field.
